title: Kinrara puchong, Selangor - Design and build new office by inter
description:
interior design project video - Interior design and build for new office lot at 2nd floor Bandar Kinrara Puchong, Selangor

Project scope: Interior design and build for new office lot at Bandar Kinrara Puchong, ceiling, flooring, partitioning, wiring, networking and carpentry works.

Size: New empty office lot 4500sf at 2nd floor

Capacity: 1 x meeting room for 10pax, 1 x MD room, 1 x Finance room, 1 x account room, 1 x server room, 1 x monitoring room, 1 x prayer room and 16 workstation.
